Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.35,1:22:24.05,sub,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小光
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.25,1:22:45.25,sub,,0,0,0,,查姆 查姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.05,1:22:56.75,sub,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 查姆 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.65,1:23:22.15,sub,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.95,1:23:25.55,sub,,0,0,0,,沙巴达巴
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.85,1:23:29.55,sub,,0,0,0,,你竟敢…
